tasks.details:
Modify the UserProfile interface to include:
- profilePicture: string (URL to avatar image)
- avatarDescription: string (text description of avatar appearance)
- level: number (current user level)
- xp: number (current experience points)
- totalXp: number (xp required for next level)
- achievements: Achievement[] (array of achievement objects)
- socialConnections: Connection[] (array of connected users)
- communityMemberships: Community[] (array of communities)
- surveyHistory: CompletedSurvey[] (array of completed surveys)

Create additional interfaces as needed:
